{
  "stem": "2533.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's where the gas chambers, or they were executed before even that, shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day when I was still sorting, a-- a boy-- call him a boy, he maybe was 17 or 18.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He hid a can of sardines.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the Scharfuhrers, one of the Germans, saw it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He took him out and shot him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He said that's only for the German army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even when we used to find something, that-- like biscuits, or people were bringing food with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were coming from all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had to so discreetly put things into our mouth, not to chew, because if they'd see that, that was the end.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were not allowed to do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- I didn't want to hide it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want-- I knew, you know, if they found it-- and-- And the-- the only-- the-- the-- transports who used to come from part of Europe.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were most in cattle train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But from France, the transport, they used to come in passenger trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were still nicely dressed up, and they even had suitcases.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they even tried to give some money for the people who were working on there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were called the Bahnhofkommando.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were helping the people to get off of the trains.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- they were not clobbered like from other parts of Europe, the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they climbed down with the suitcases.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were even trying to pay for the ones who helped them, give them some money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were told to put the suitcase-- they were given numbers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were told put the suitcases on a place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they undressed, and they were going for-- for health reasons to-- to have a shower.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
